snippet.title: Holbrook Hotel [RELEASE TRAILER]
snippet.description: Holbrook Hotel is an atmospheric horror game about the killer in Holbrook Oaks. After hearing a noise in the neighboring hotel room, you start a short adventure around the town. Escape the man, and get to saftey, if there is any. Play for $1.99 on Itch.io: https://bare-bones.itch.io/holbrook-hotel
